{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":231,"text":"So yesterday, I was out in the street"},{"time":2611,"text":"in front of this building,"},{"time":5287,"text":"and I was walking down the sidewalk,"},{"time":8323,"text":"and I had company, several of us,"},{"time":10183,"text":"and we were all abiding by the rules"},{"time":11681,"text":"of walking down sidewalks."},{"time":14068,"text":"We're not talking each other. We're facing forward."},{"time":16510,"text":"We're moving."},{"time":17933,"text":"When the person in front of me slows down."},{"time":21196,"text":"And so I'm watching him, and he slows down,"},{"time":23186,"text":"and finally he stops."},{"time":24783,"text":"Well, that wasn't fast enough for me,"},{"time":26868,"text":"so I put on my turn signal, and I walked around him,"},{"time":30547,"text":"and as I walked, I looked to see what he was doing,"},{"time":33280,"text":"and he was doing this."},{"time":35848,"text":"He was texting,"},{"time":37792,"text":"and he couldn't text and walk at the same time."},{"time":39814,"text":"Now we could approach this"},{"time":41623,"text":"from a working memory perspective"},{"time":43515,"text":"or from a multitasking perspective."},{"time":45500,"text":"We're going to do working memory today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":48029,"text":"Now, working memory"},{"time":50169,"text":"is that part of our consciousness that we are"},{"time":53317,"text":"aware of at any given time of day."},{"time":55771,"text":"You're going it right now."},{"time":57413,"text":"It's not something we can turn off."},{"time":59067,"text":"If you turn it off, that's called a coma, okay?"},{"time":62518,"text":"So right now, you're doing just fine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":65621,"text":"Now working memory has four basic components."},{"time":67977,"text":"It allows us to store some immediate experiences"},{"time":70574,"text":"and a little bit of knowledge."},{"time":72190,"text":"It allows us to reach back\ninto our long-term memory"},{"time":75559,"text":"and pull some of that in as we need it,"},{"time":77409,"text":"mixes it, processes it"},{"time":79609,"text":"in light of whatever our current goal is."},{"time":81903,"text":"Now the current goal isn't something like,"},{"time":83417,"text":"I want to be president or the best surfer in the world."},{"time":85699,"text":"It's more mundane. I'd like that cookie,"},{"time":88502,"text":"or I need to figure out how to get into my hotel room."},{"time":91104,"text":"Now working memory capacity"},{"time":93284,"text":"is our ability to leverage that,"},{"time":95890,"text":"our ability to take what we know"},{"time":98685,"text":"and what we can hang onto"},{"time":99961,"text":"and leverage it in ways that allow us to satisfy"},{"time":103560,"text":"our current goal."}]},{"cues":[{"time":105310,"text":"Now working memory capacity"},{"time":107094,"text":"has a fairly long history,"},{"time":109147,"text":"and it's associated with a lot of positive effects."},{"time":111346,"text":"People with high working memory capacity"},{"time":113734,"text":"tend to be good storytellers."},{"time":115978,"text":"They tend to solve and do well\non standardized tests,"},{"time":119955,"text":"however important that is."},{"time":122300,"text":"They're able to have high levels of writing ability."},{"time":126083,"text":"They're also able to reason at high levels."}]},{"cues":[{"time":128957,"text":"So what we're going to do here\nis play a little bit with some of that."},{"time":131875,"text":"So I'm going to ask you to perform a couple tasks,"},{"time":134425,"text":"and we're going to take your \nworking memory out for a ride."},{"time":137504,"text":"You up for that? Okay."}]},{"cues":[{"time":140101,"text":"I'm going to give you five words,"},{"time":142299,"text":"and I just want you to hang on to them."},{"time":144092,"text":"Don't write them down. Just hang on to them."},{"time":145960,"text":"Five words."},{"time":147372,"text":"While you're hanging on to them,\nI'm going to ask you to answer three questions."},{"time":150575,"text":"I want to see what happens with those words."},{"time":152480,"text":"So here's the words:"},{"time":154327,"text":"tree,"},{"time":157615,"text":"highway,"},{"time":160550,"text":"mirror,"},{"time":162928,"text":"Saturn"},{"time":165060,"text":"and electrode."},{"time":167479,"text":"So far so good?"},{"time":169063,"text":"Okay. What I want you to do"},{"time":170917,"text":"is I want you to tell me what the answer is"},{"time":174264,"text":"to 23 times eight."},{"time":176586,"text":"Just shout it out."},{"time":180766,"text":"(Mumbling) (Laughter)"},{"time":184468,"text":"In fact it's -- (Mumbling) -- exactly. (Laughter)"},{"time":186889,"text":"All right. I want you to take out your left hand"},{"time":190116,"text":"and I want you to go, \"One, two, three, four, five,"},{"time":192796,"text":"six, seven, eight, nine, 10.\""},{"time":194999,"text":"It's a neurological test,\njust in case you were wondering."},{"time":197695,"text":"All right, now what I want you to do"},{"time":199560,"text":"is to recite the last five letters"},{"time":201785,"text":"of the English alphabet backwards."},{"time":206637,"text":"You should have started with Z."},{"time":208539,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":211830,"text":"All right. How many people here are still pretty sure"},{"time":213917,"text":"you've got all five words?"},{"time":216368,"text":"Okay. Typically we end up with about less than half,"},{"time":219549,"text":"right, which is normal. There will be a range."},{"time":221624,"text":"Some people can hang on to five."},{"time":223180,"text":"Some people can hang on to 10."},{"time":224464,"text":"Some will be down to two or three."}]},{"cues":[{"time":226769,"text":"What we know is this is really important\nto the way we function, right?"},{"time":230173,"text":"And it's going to be really important here at TED"},{"time":232121,"text":"because you're going to be exposed\nto so many different ideas."}]},{"cues":[{"time":235157,"text":"Now the problem that we have"},{"time":237364,"text":"is that life comes at us,"},{"time":239076,"text":"and it comes at us very quickly,"},{"time":241193,"text":"and what we need to do is to take that amorphous"},{"time":245106,"text":"flow of experience and somehow"},{"time":246884,"text":"extract meaning from it"},{"time":248391,"text":"with a working memory"},{"time":249690,"text":"that's about the size of a pea."},{"time":251959,"text":"Now don't get me wrong,\nworking memory is awesome."},{"time":254506,"text":"Working memory allows us"},{"time":256621,"text":"to investigate our current experience"},{"time":258993,"text":"as we move forward."},{"time":260488,"text":"It allows us to make sense of the world around us."},{"time":263656,"text":"But it does have certain limits."}]},{"cues":[{"time":265575,"text":"Now working memory is great\nfor allowing us to communicate."},{"time":269418,"text":"We can have a conversation,"},{"time":270890,"text":"and I can build a narrative around that"},{"time":273577,"text":"so I know where we've been and where we're going"},{"time":275307,"text":"and how to contribute to this conversation."},{"time":277395,"text":"It allows us to problem-solve, critical think."},{"time":279632,"text":"We can be in the middle of a meeting,"},{"time":281436,"text":"listen to somebody's presentation, evaluate it,"},{"time":283939,"text":"decide whether or not we like it,"},{"time":285581,"text":"ask follow-up questions."},{"time":286839,"text":"All of that occurs within working memory."},{"time":290209,"text":"It also allows us to go to the store"},{"time":292056,"text":"and allows us to get milk and eggs and cheese"},{"time":295710,"text":"when what we're really looking for"},{"time":297481,"text":"is Red Bull and bacon. (Laughter)"},{"time":300318,"text":"Gotta make sure we're getting what we're looking for."},{"time":303040,"text":"Now, a central issue with working memory"},{"time":306377,"text":"is that it's limited."},{"time":307774,"text":"It's limited in capacity, limited in duration,"},{"time":309970,"text":"limited in focus."},{"time":311580,"text":"We tend to remember about four things."},{"time":314315,"text":"Okay? It used to be seven,"},{"time":316212,"text":"but with functional MRIs, apparently it's four,"},{"time":318236,"text":"and we were overachieving."},{"time":320779,"text":"Now we can remember those four things"},{"time":322752,"text":"for about 10 to 20 seconds"},{"time":324615,"text":"unless we do something with it,"},{"time":326342,"text":"unless we process it,\nunless we apply it to something,"},{"time":328855,"text":"unless we talk to somebody about it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":332500,"text":"When we think about working memory,"},{"time":335742,"text":"we have to realize that this limited capacity"},{"time":339046,"text":"has lots of different impacts on us."},{"time":341541,"text":"Have you ever walked from one room to another"},{"time":344566,"text":"and then forgotten why you're there?"},{"time":347577,"text":"You do know the solution to that, right?"},{"time":349746,"text":"You go back to that original room. (Laughter)"},{"time":352092,"text":"Have you ever forgotten your keys?"},{"time":356029,"text":"You ever forgotten your car?"},{"time":358558,"text":"You ever forgotten your kids?"},{"time":361529,"text":"Have you ever been involved in a conversation,"},{"time":363718,"text":"and you realize that the conversation to your left"},{"time":365662,"text":"is actually more interesting? (Laughter)"},{"time":368496,"text":"So you're nodding and you're smiling,"},{"time":370120,"text":"but you're really paying attention\nto this one over here,"},{"time":372508,"text":"until you hear that last word go up,"},{"time":374808,"text":"and you realize,"},{"time":376468,"text":"you've been asked a question. (Laughter)"},{"time":379422,"text":"And you're really hoping the answer is no,"},{"time":381369,"text":"because that's what you're about to say."},{"time":384588,"text":"All of that talks about working memory,"},{"time":387064,"text":"what we can do and what we can't do."},{"time":389322,"text":"We need to realize that working memory"},{"time":390859,"text":"has a limited capacity,"},{"time":392258,"text":"and that working memory capacity itself\nis how we negotiate that."},{"time":395777,"text":"We negotiate that through strategies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":397948,"text":"So what I want to do is talk a little bit\nabout a couple of strategies here,"},{"time":400269,"text":"and these will be really important"},{"time":401544,"text":"because you are now in an\ninformation target-rich environment"},{"time":405299,"text":"for the next several days."},{"time":407419,"text":"Now the first part of this that we need to think about"},{"time":410323,"text":"and we need to process our existence, our life,"},{"time":413090,"text":"immediately and repeatedly."},{"time":414805,"text":"We need to process what's going on"},{"time":417246,"text":"the moment it happens, not 10 minutes later,"},{"time":420160,"text":"not a week later, at the moment."},{"time":422429,"text":"So we need to think about, well,\ndo I agree with him?"},{"time":426162,"text":"What's missing? What would I like to know?"},{"time":428942,"text":"Do I agree with the assumptions?"},{"time":431164,"text":"How can I apply this in my life?"},{"time":432974,"text":"It's a way of processing what's going on"},{"time":434954,"text":"so that we can use it later."},{"time":436721,"text":"Now we also need to repeat it. We need to practice."},{"time":439681,"text":"So we need to think about it here."},{"time":442093,"text":"In between, we want to talk to people about it."},{"time":444888,"text":"We're going to write it down,\nand when you get home,"},{"time":447111,"text":"pull out those notes and think about them"},{"time":449071,"text":"and end up practicing over time."},{"time":451460,"text":"Practice for some reason\nbecame a very negative thing."},{"time":454011,"text":"It's very positive."}]},{"cues":[{"time":455463,"text":"The next thing is, we need to think elaboratively"},{"time":458513,"text":"and we need to think illustratively."},{"time":460853,"text":"Oftentimes, we think that we have to relate\nnew knowledge to prior knowledge."},{"time":464307,"text":"What we want to do is spin that around."},{"time":466237,"text":"We want to take all of our existence"},{"time":467994,"text":"and wrap it around that new knowledge"},{"time":469747,"text":"and make all of these connections\nand it becomes more meaningful."},{"time":473195,"text":"We also want to use imagery.\nWe are built for images."},{"time":476989,"text":"We need to take advantage of that."},{"time":478847,"text":"Think about things in images,"},{"time":480357,"text":"write things down that way."},{"time":482706,"text":"If you read a book, pull things up."},{"time":484268,"text":"I just got through reading \"The Great Gatsby,\""},{"time":486321,"text":"and I have a perfect idea of what he looks like"},{"time":489420,"text":"in my head, so my own version."}]},{"cues":[{"time":492418,"text":"The last one is organization and support."},{"time":494421,"text":"We are meaning-making machines. It's what we do."},{"time":496990,"text":"We try to make meaning out of\neverything that happens to us."},{"time":500131,"text":"Organization helps, so we need to structure"},{"time":502421,"text":"what we're doing in ways that make sense."},{"time":504000,"text":"If we are providing knowledge and experience,"},{"time":506586,"text":"we need to structure that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":508071,"text":"And the last one is support."},{"time":510570,"text":"We all started as novices."},{"time":512292,"text":"Everything we do is an\napproximation of sophistication."},{"time":515333,"text":"We should expect it to change over time.\nWe have to support that."},{"time":518270,"text":"The support may come in asking people questions,"},{"time":520926,"text":"giving them a sheet of paper that has\nan organizational chart on it"},{"time":524429,"text":"or has some guiding images,"},{"time":526977,"text":"but we need to support it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":528877,"text":"Now, the final piece of this, the take-home message"},{"time":534168,"text":"from a working memory capacity standpoint is this:"},{"time":537094,"text":"what we process, we learn."},{"time":540025,"text":"If we're not processing life, we're not living it."},{"time":544826,"text":"Live life. Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":546718,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}